                            <comment id="15291582" author="bryanc" created="Thu, 19 May 2016 17:24:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this looks to be a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-15332&quot; title=&quot;OutOfMemory in TimSort &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-15332&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-15332&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15300529" author="rxin" created="Wed, 25 May 2016 17:59:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We should look into this &amp;#8211; do proper memory management for timsort buffers.&lt;/p&gt;

